{
  "info": {
    "name": "MindUp Sprint-1 Backend (Production)",
    "_postman_id": "91f7fd5e-fad3-469a-8d63-087f88fa99d3",
    "description": "## How to get a Clerk JWT token for testing\n\n**Option A — Easiest: use the `get_clerk_token.html` helper page**\n1. Open `postman/get_clerk_token.html` in your browser\n2. Sign in with your student account\n3. Copy the token shown on screen\n4. In Postman → Edit this collection → Variables → paste it as the value for `clerk_token`\n\n**Option B — From browser DevTools**\n1. Open your frontend app and sign in\n2. DevTools → Network tab → click any request → copy the `Authorization: Bearer eyJ...` value (just the `eyJ...` part)\n3. Paste it as the `clerk_token` collection variable\n\n**Option C — From browser console (if frontend uses Clerk JS SDK)**\n```js\nawait window.Clerk.session.getToken()\n```\n\n> **Note:** Tokens expire after ~1 hour. Refresh as needed.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000"
    },
    {
      "key": "clerk_token",
      "value": "PASTE_YOUR_CLERK_JWT_HERE",
      "description": "Clerk JWT — see collection description for how to get one"
    },
    {
      "key": "adminApiKey",
      "value": "change-me",
      "description": "Must match ADMIN_API_KEY in .env"
    },
    {
      "key": "provinceId",
      "value": "1"
    },
    {
      "key": "districtId",
      "value": "1"
    },
    {
      "key": "gradeId",
      "value": "1"
    },
    {
      "key": "subjectId",
      "value": "1"
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{clerk_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔓 Meta (no auth needed)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List provinces",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/meta/provinces"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List districts by province",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/meta/districts?province_id={{provinceId}}"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List grades",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/meta/grades"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List avatars",
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/meta/avatars"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🎓 Me — Student Profile",
      "description": "All requests in this folder use the collection-level Bearer token (clerk_token variable).",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get my profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me/profile"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Complete onboarding",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              },
              "raw": "{\n  \"full_name\": \"Test Student\",\n  \"username\": \"test_student_prod1\",\n  \"grade_id\": {{gradeId}},\n  \"province_id\": {{provinceId}},\n  \"district_id\": {{districtId}},\n  \"avatar_key\": \"avatar_1\",\n  \"subject_ids\": [1, 2]\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me/onboarding"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update profile — full name",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              },
              "raw": "{\n  \"full_name\": \"Updated Name\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me/profile"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update profile — username",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              },
              "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"new_username_99\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me/profile"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update profile — avatar",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              },
              "raw": "{\n  \"avatar_key\": \"avatar_3\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me/profile"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update profile — grade + district",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              },
              "raw": "{\n  \"grade_id\": {{gradeId}},\n  \"province_id\": {{provinceId}},\n  \"district_id\": {{districtId}}\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/me/profile"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
